{"tid":1543230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請救救天頌苑居民 (長文 慎入 宣傳)","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:07.000Z","uid":44499,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5499aafc6bbc169b2e44eab38aab213e502e05a","tid":1543230,"uid":44499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"本人是借朋友AC的,第一次開POST,如有不足之處請多多包涵,謝謝!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                                                                                                                                                                           想改變現況又不知從何入手既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請救救天頌苑居民<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野係好多香港人身邊正正發生緊<br />\n不止係一個屋苑<br />\n越黎越多年輕人開始醒覺 關心政治<br />\n有唔少人留意到身邊既家人長輩係反對自己而家做既野，而且唔少係建制派既支持者<br />\n點解有成二百萬人上街高叫口號既同時<br />\n家裡每天見的親人為什麼不明白我們<br />\n議會入面建制派仍然佔有大多議席<br />\n先唔講功能組別這個問題<br />\n除了一車車既老人院掌心雷<br />\n日常生活當中其實滲透左係我地身邊而大家都唔知<br />\n有沒有想過每天回家在樓下等𨋢的時候看的通告<br />\n原來背後係有幕後黑手<br />\n平常沒有為意那些公告上面看似平凡的屋苑活動 什麼一日遊<br />\n原來就係今日令到你屋企人變成藍絲<br />\n甚至成為建制派既票倉<br />\n如果佢地明目張膽寫明禮義廉既活動<br />\n你當然一早就出手阻止左啦<br />\n但佢地鼠竊狗偷 防不勝防<br />\n就算屋企人無參加過呢啲活動<br />\n佢地仍有很多途徑去接觸你屋企人 <br />\n在屋苑裡寫什麼的揮春 派什麼的月餅等等<br />\n<br />\n唔比黑衣服的住戶回家 偷偷更改大門密碼<br />\n隨時可以發生在自己身上<br />\n因為佢地有權力去幫你選擇一間咩既管理公司<br />\n<br />\n以下的圖片是天水圍一個屋苑發生緊既事<br />\n香港人 怎會願意有人用自己屋苑名義<br />\n代表著自己和這個從小長大的屋苑裡的鄰居<br />\n去發表香港人暴徒論 去維護721恐怖襲擊既白衣人<br />\n<br />\n要光復香港 可以從自己住的地方開始<br />\n<br />\n一班住係天頌苑的香港人希望改變現況<br />\n希望光復天頌 踢走建制派<br />\n因為<br />\n到今天仍有很多維修合約被圍標<br />\n當中涉及的利益輸送不得而知<br />\n被管理處掌控授權票，被房署玩弄於手中<br />\n而家天頌苑既管理公司<br />\n正正就係麗晶花園同一間管理公司<br />\n唔希望黑警既濫捕有日發生在天頌學生身上<br />\n最近還加裝了很多的cctv在邨內行人路上<br />\n目的顯然易見<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫忙按下分享 讓更多屯天元的朋友看到<br />\n因為他們很有機會接觸到身邊有人住係呢個屋苑<br />\n<br />\n📣9月8日 天頌業主會議<br />\n<br />\n好好利用你的 *授權票*<br />\n<br />\n自己屋苑自己救<br />\n<br />\n多一票已經很多<br />\n<br />\n以下是在這個我愛天頌的專頁裡cap圖出來<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2073061539656244/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2073061539656244%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=e2db54e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2073061539656244/?ref=share</a><br />\n<br />\n#光復香港時代革命<br />\n#香港人加油<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n更重要的是<br />\n我們一個都不能再少🙏🏻<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6qgFmX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6qgFmX.jpg&h=4973a8f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74cda2edf9964a61a02b50680b045409e3e21337","tid":1543230,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b333a17c33cb0d326b09120ba348069fb3cef513","tid":1543230,"uid":44499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"2b1a89f7c28d667e2c05a9b1d31979e940c2a757","tid":1543230,"uid":44499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"785d0b031f9c497b041b5c9fba3a5db86db301e9","tid":1543230,"uid":44499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:37:35.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"7305c7ec934c382fe914907332113d48f0fae29d","tid":1543230,"uid":44499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"ddeb0ef43590fd8be2d7a553a63eb8527dc554cd","tid":1543230,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"果到本身班業主立案法團都解散左<br />\n<br />\n區議員投票冇問題 問題係冇掂既區議員出黎選<br />\n<br />\n至於個法團個個R著數先做 而家仲要冇人出黎做叫房署廷任<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句今日咁既結果都係大家自己攞黎<br />\n<br />\n就算晚晚係咁叫 但都係冇人有心組織法團搞好屋苑 哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add0e81eb526517e8bf93338a45c03dbe0ce5d79","tid":1543230,"uid":44499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"907bdd79c9ba2624f66daf16edf2f919a05e6394","tid":1543230,"uid":52271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"呢d組織一向係建制樁腳黎<br />\n其實支那用香港人嘅資源（地區撥款，因為區會主席係建制）去宣傳支那，令香港人冇掟企<br />\n大家睇返劉細良響朵嗰段片就明白"},{"pid":"5cc33760cca9e98fdb54621af56b40095535046d","tid":1543230,"uid":22637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9e5241f236aebf64f6ca